<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-06-1198 </DOCNO><TEXT>Arthur D. Little, Inc. was commissioned by the Maryland Power Plant ResearchProgram to undertake a study to perform a critique of current PPSP electricitysales and peak-demand forecasting methodologies; identify a possibleset of alternative forecasting methods and models that could provideimproved forecasting accuracy; and to recommend to the PPSP methodologicalimprovements that would assist the PPSP in achieving its goals. The reportsummarizes the study.</TEXT></DOC>